Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.53,0:05:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是他们发现他身上有钱  会杀了他的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If they find cash on him, they'll kill him.
