Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.93,0:05:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他曾是我们在七十年代最早的一批间谍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He was a primary asset for us in the '70s.
