Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.67,0:06:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一向这么做  这是我们的行事手段\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's how we do business. It's what we do.
