Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.30,0:06:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别问我  沃利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't look at me, Wally.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.23,0:06:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿高工资的人是你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's why they pay you the big bucks.
