Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.91,0:06:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉莫斯科分站往下行动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tell Moscow to move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.66,0:06:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有信息及时汇报\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And keep me updated.
