Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.98,0:07:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰克  我不是第一次行动了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jack, I've done this before.
