Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.06,0:12:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没消息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nothing yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.79,0:12:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-有情况就通知我  -好  第一个通知你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Keep me informed. - Yeah, first to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.04,0:12:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.12,0:13:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我手快被你们扭断了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're breaking my arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.20,0:13:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我最新情况\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Get me up to speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.37,0:13:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正在跟巨锚做资金传递\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We were proceeding with the dead drop for GT Weigh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.64,0:13:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廖内德·波列修克  克格勃官员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}KGB officer Leonid Poleshchuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.59,0:14:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只说暗号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Encrypted names only.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少他还是个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, for crying out loud, he's a human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.69,0:14:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟  守点规矩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Arthur. Follow protocol.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.00,0:14:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨锚的行动地点是在彼得罗夫斯基公园\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}For GT Weigh in our operational location in Petrovsky park.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.52,0:14:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的情报专员开始行动的时间是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our case officer started the operation at...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.45,0:14:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格林威治时间  14点20分\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}14:20, GMT.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.23,0:14:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前我被告知他有两个小时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was told he had two hours
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.32,0:14:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-来避开侦查掩护自己  -结果呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- to evade detection and go black. - And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.74,0:14:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他没能向站长复命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He never reported back to his station chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.65,0:14:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一个联系我们的是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Who was first contact to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.44,0:14:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情报专员的妻子上报了他没回家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The case officer's wife reported that he hadn't returned home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.22,0:14:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What time was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.95,0:14:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格林威治时间  18点30分\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}18:30, GMT.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.37,0:14:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他花了两个小时伪装掩护\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So he took two hours to go black,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.40,0:14:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把钱放进情报点  然后被抓\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}filled the drop, was arrested,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.22,0:14:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后他妻子等了足足两个小时才联系我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and his wife took an extra two hours grace time and called us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.26,0:14:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对事实吧  大伙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We need to face facts here, people --
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.62,0:14:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们包抄了我们的情报专员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They rolled up our case officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可能他们知道他为什么会在那\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They probably know why he was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.55,0:14:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这意味着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨锚招供了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}GT weigh's been compromised.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.26,0:14:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早和你说了  这主意糟糕透顶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Told you. This was a really bad idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.70,0:14:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里克  现在不是怪罪别人的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Rick, not the moment for blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,线报员是否已招供  只是我们单方面的猜测\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Whether our asset has been compromised is a guess on our part.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.67,0:14:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可这猜测相当有说服力  华莱士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Seems like an educated guess, Wallace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.37,0:14:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先集中注意力在已有的确定情报上吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let's just focus on what we know for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.55,0:14:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情报专员现在在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where's our case officer now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.02,0:15:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们认为他被关押在卢比扬卡监狱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We believe he's being held in Lubyanka prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.89,0:15:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通知国务院\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Notify the State Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.37,0:15:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知会美国驻俄大使\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Wake up the U.S. ambassador.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.51,0:15:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}卢比扬卡监狱\N苏联
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.42,0:15:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我  我是一名美国外交官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Get your hands off me! I am an American diplomat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.37,0:15:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任职于美国大使馆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I work -- I work at the U.S. embassy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.82,0:15:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是美国的外交官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am an American diplomat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.15,0:15:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任职于美国大使馆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I work at the U.S. embassy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.17,0:15:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20,000卢布\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}20,000 rubles.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.71,0:15:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好大一笔钱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's a lot of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.07,0:15:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是一名美国外交官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm an American diplomat
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.79,0:15:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任职于美国大使馆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}working at the U.S. embassy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.13,0:15:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在此要求通知美国大使\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I hereby request that you call the U.S. ambassador
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.76,0:15:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并告知他我受到非法拘禁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and alert him to this illegal detention.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.49,0:15:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.77,0:15:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们来说说什么是合法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let's talk of legality.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一个美国公民\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You are American citizen
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.27,0:15:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却在莫斯科市中心的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}leaving 20,000 rubles
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.20,0:15:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一处水泥缺口里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in piece of broken concrete...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:16:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞了两万卢布\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in downtown Moscow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使翻遍所有苏联法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}By any reading of Soviet Law,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.44,0:16:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都会被指认为犯罪活动预谋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that speaks to impending criminal activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.17,0:16:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,介意解释一下吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You care to explain?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.90,0:16:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是一名美国外交官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm an American diplomat,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.16,0:16:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任职于美国大使馆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}working at the U.S. embassy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.94,0:16:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许是为了一个女人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Perhaps it was for a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.16,0:16:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有爱上过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Have you fallen in love
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.94,0:16:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某位俄罗斯美人呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}with one of our Russian beauties?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.80,0:16:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情妇呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hmm? A mistress? Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.15,0:16:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她希望你能来照顾她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She wants you to take care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.82,0:16:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是个...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.19,0:16:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听上去挺可信的故事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}plausible cover story.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.89,0:16:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.51,0:16:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者我们彼此敞开天窗说亮话吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Or shall we just be honest with each other? Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.58,0:16:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是什么美国外交官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You are no more American diplomat
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.70,0:16:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我也不是拉达工厂的工人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}than I am comrade worker in Lada factory!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.26,0:16:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都是间谍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We are both spies!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.55,0:16:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你被我逮了个现行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And I caught you spying!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.40,0:17:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.92,0:17:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要摆脱目前的处境  回到你家人身边\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}all you really have to do to make this all better,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.60,0:17:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真正要做的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to be released to your family,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.52,0:17:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指认我们逮捕的那个男人是你的间谍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}is confirm that the man we arrested was your asset.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.73,0:18:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有话直说  格莱姆斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey. Spit it out, Grimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.08,0:18:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的情报专员正在蹲大牢呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our case officer's sitting in a prison cell right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.78,0:18:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天知道克格勃会怎么拷问他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}God only knows how the KGB is interrogating him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.51,0:18:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会打电话给国务院  让他们提出抗议\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll call the State Department, they'll scream and yell,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.49,0:18:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他从牢里弄出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and we'll get him out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.67,0:18:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你真正担心的不是这个  是不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But that's not what you're really worried about, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.45,0:18:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个间谍  波列修克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The asset -- Poleshchuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.23,0:18:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和他一起在巴拿马待过一个月\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I spent a month with him in Panama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.07,0:18:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他粗鲁不堪  整日酗酒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Wild man, drank like a fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.97,0:18:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我渐渐开始喜欢他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But I grew to like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.63,0:18:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他给我讲过一个故事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He told me this story,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.43,0:18:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说他想要用一瓶威士忌\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}said he wanted to bribe a potential recruit
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.63,0:18:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收买一名潜在间谍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}with a bottle of whiskey,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.63,0:18:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他的克格勃上司拒绝付账\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but his KGB boss wouldn't pay for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.67,0:18:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他对此耿耿于怀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That stuck in his craw so bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.14,0:18:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天  他自愿加入了中情局\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the next day, he volunteered for the CIA.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.27,0:18:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可能是我们唯一一个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's probably the only spy we ever got
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.88,0:18:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只用一瓶酒就买通了的间谍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}for a single bottle of booze.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.17,0:18:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能说错了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well... I could be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.09,0:18:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们无法确定他是否已经招供\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We can't be sure he's been compromised.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.58,0:18:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波列修克有老婆和孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Poleshchuk has a wife and children.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.43,0:18:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他知道他在做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He knew what he was getting into.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.48,0:18:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  你确定吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Did he? Are you so sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.32,0:18:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们会把他拖到冒牌法官面前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They'll haul him in front of a phony judge,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.87,0:18:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行模拟审讯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}they'll stage a mock trial,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.69,0:19:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行宣判  判他有罪  然后...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}pronounce him guilty, sentence him, and then --
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.10,0:19:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们会把他拖到院子里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They'll drag him out into a courtyard
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.67,0:19:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,执行枪决\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and put a bullet in the back of his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊蒂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sandy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.62,0:19:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是你的错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.36,0:19:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我坚持要他把钱藏在苏联境内\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I pushed to have him dead-drop the money inside the USSR.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.29,0:19:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是我  也许他现在已经自由\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If I hadn't, maybe he'd be free now,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.26,0:19:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正和他的家人团聚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}home with his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.13,0:19:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做的是对的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It was the right thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.02,0:19:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但事情搞砸了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But it blew up on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.20,0:19:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前为止我们还不知道为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And we have no idea why yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.02,0:19:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格莱姆斯  继续你的工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Grimes, you stay on task.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.25,0:19:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得努力工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You keep your nose to the grindstone,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.67,0:19:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但最重要的是  你要把生活中的一切分开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but mostly you keep everything in your life separate --
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作  家庭  间谍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Work, family, assets.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.03,0:19:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必须把它们分开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You have got to compartmentalize.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.64,0:19:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道我能不能做到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't know if I can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.51,0:19:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道我是不是那样的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't know if I'm that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.21,0:19:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你做不到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well... If you can't,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.83,0:19:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份工作会毁了你的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}this job will tear you apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.31,0:20:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整个克格勃大楼里  只有一个地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There is only one place to have a private conversation
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.45,0:20:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能进行秘密谈话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in entire KGB building.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.54,0:20:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}巴拿马\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}1972
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.81,0:20:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道在哪吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And do you know where that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.83,0:20:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}男厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.99,0:20:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}没错  厕所是我们完成本职工作的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.12,0:20:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在酒吧里大声谈及你雇主的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Broadcasting the name of your employer in a bar
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.93,0:20:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不是个明智的举动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}might not be the smartest move.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.43,0:20:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许我们应该换个地方接着谈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maybe we should take this conversation someplace else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.11,0:20:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我  我们会是最佳间谍组合\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You and I, we could be the best spy team.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.61,0:20:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就我们俩  去巴黎或是塔西提岛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just the two of us -- Paris or maybe Tahiti.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.36,0:20:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不这么想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.18,0:20:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我不尝试一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I would be haunted forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会一辈子心里不安的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}if I didn't at least try.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.90,0:21:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}美国大使馆\N莫斯科
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.40,0:21:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我们使馆的工作人员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's part of my diplomatic staff
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.35,0:21:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依照国际法  拥有豁免权\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and, by international law, has immunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.92,0:21:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵方触犯了苏维埃社会主义共和联盟的法律\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You have violated the laws and integrity
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.00,0:21:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威胁到我国领土完整\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}of the Union of Soviet Socialist --
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.80,0:21:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我方绝对尊重\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have absolute respect
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.77,0:21:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苏联的领土完整\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}for the territorial integrity of the Soviet Union.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.55,0:21:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并竭尽全力遵守贵国的法律\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We make every attempt to abide by your sovereign laws.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.75,0:21:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说谎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You are lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.66,0:21:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们知道贵国在我国进行间谍活动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We know you run spies in my country.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.74,0:21:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一行为是对苏联的严重侮辱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is a terrible insult to the Soviet Union.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.13,0:21:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们绝不会把间谍安插在贵国主权范围...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We would not employ a spy within the sovereign borders of --
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.13,0:21:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两万卢布显然是用来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}20,000 rubles was obviously...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.03,0:21:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-这不是问题的关键  -通过行贿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- That is not the issue here. - A bribe...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.45,0:21:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以策反我国公民卖国通敌\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to get our citizens to betray their country.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.00,0:21:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果别无选择的话  我会寻求白宫介入的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If I have to get the white house involved, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.72,0:21:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他挂电话了  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I believe he hung up, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.51,0:21:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}卢比扬卡监狱  苏联
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.89,0:22:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你的拘留到此为止了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You are being released from detention.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.80,0:22:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过对你的指控依旧成立\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The charges against you still stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.53,0:22:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从此刻起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}From this moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.93,0:22:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经被我苏联列为不受欢迎者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you are persona non grata in Soviet Union.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.14,0:22:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,限你两个小时之内收拾个人物品\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You have two hours to collect your belongings
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.43,0:22:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开我国\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and leave the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.28,0:22:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一份就此事件的通知已经发往你们的大使馆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A letter to this effect has been sent to your embassy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.87,0:22:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就在这  是不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's here, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.15,0:22:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这栋楼里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.61,0:22:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被关在另一间牢房\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In another cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.14,0:22:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们俄国人对卢比扬卡监狱流传着一种说法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Russians have saying about Lubyanka prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.49,0:22:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说这是莫斯科最高的建筑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They call it the tallest building in Moscow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.13,0:22:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道为什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.80,0:23:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为从地下室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because, from the basement,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.03,0:23:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就可以一眼望到西伯利亚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you can see all the way to Siberia.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.50,0:23:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的情报专员已被从卢比扬卡监狱释放\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our case officer has been released from Lubyanka.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.81,0:23:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有两个小时离开俄国\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He has two hours to leave the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.28,0:23:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俄国佬正在把他押上飞机\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're putting him on a plane right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.67,0:23:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.96,0:23:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是避免了一场危机\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}One crisis averted.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.18,0:23:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会给所有站长拍份电报\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll write to all station chiefs.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.40,0:23:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉他们之前是你负责巨锚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You handled GT Weigh in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.03,0:23:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并警告有一定可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let them know there's a possibility
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.34,0:23:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-他是被出卖的  -好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- He's been compromised. - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.68,0:23:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊蒂还有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And, Sandy...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.87,0:23:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}巨锚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.33,0:23:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫他们再次核查各站的行动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ask them to double check their operations.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.29,0:23:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何有机密权限的职员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Employees with access,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.76,0:23:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通信  情报手段\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Communications, tradecraft --
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.21,0:23:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何方面只要是出一点差错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Compromise could have come from anywhere --
