Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.75,0:29:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高兴再次见到你  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's good to see you again, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.42,0:29:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长官  正如你所知\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sir, as you probably know,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.63,0:29:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们与巨锚的情报投送\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our dead drop to GT Weigh
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.92,0:29:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两天前在莫斯科被截击了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}was intercepted two days ago in Moscow.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.58,0:29:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的情报专员被捕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our case officer was arrested,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.18,0:29:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有理由相信我们的谍报员被出卖了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and we had reason to believe our asset had been compromised.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.70,0:29:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚  我们得到可靠消息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Last night, we learned with certainty
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.30,0:29:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨锚在卢比扬卡监狱被处决了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that GT Weigh had been executed in Lubyanka prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.45,0:29:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正在对此事件展开调查\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're now beginning the process of investigating the nature --
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.68,0:29:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打断一下  珊蒂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let me stop you there, Sandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.11,0:29:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找借口把你叫来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I brought you here under slightly false pretenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.84,0:29:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得中情局局长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}While I do want the D.C.I.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.22,0:29:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要听到的是这次行动的细节\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to hear the details of the operation,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.37,0:29:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更重要的是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}more importantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.34,0:29:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有想要告诉你的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wanted to fill you all in on something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.84,0:30:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨锚的牺牲只是冰山一角\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The compromise of GT Weigh is just the tip of the iceberg.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.73,0:30:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况比你想象的严重得多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The situation is far worse than you can possibly imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.99,0:30:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在过去的三个月里  我们损失了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We've lost more assets in the last three months
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.97,0:30:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比史上任何时候都要多的谍报员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}than at practically any other time in our history.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.23,0:30:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨涛是一个极其成功的窃听器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Gt Taw was an extremely successful tap
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.58,0:30:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它被安装在一条位于莫斯科市中心地下的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we'd been running on a KGB phone line underground
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.84,0:30:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克格勃电话线路上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in central Moscow.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.59,0:30:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一机密保密级别很高\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It was a highly restricted case.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.19,0:30:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有极少数人知道它的存在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Very few people knew about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.46,0:30:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,线路很难接入\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The line was difficult to access,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.46,0:30:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们从那条线路得到的信息是无价的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but the intel we gained on it was invaluable --
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.22,0:30:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行动的详细计划  涉及官员姓名\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}operational detail, officer names,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.67,0:30:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地址  还有克格勃的战略情报\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}locations, KGB strategic intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.54,0:30:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三个月之前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Three months ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.77,0:30:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当一名特工人员从监听线路上取回录音带时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}while an officer was retrieving tapes from a tapped line,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.08,0:30:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警报被触发了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}an alarm sounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.31,0:30:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们安装报警装置是为了提醒情报专员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We had set up the alarm to warn case officers
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.73,0:30:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦监听线路被人发现\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in case the tap had become compromised,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.30,0:30:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果果不其然\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}which it had.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.06,0:30:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那只是开始\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That was just the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.95,0:31:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上个月\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Last month,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.64,0:31:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在慕尼黑工作了很长时间的间谍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}a longtime asset for us in Munich
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.71,0:31:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到克格勃让其返回莫斯科的指令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}was recalled by the KGB to Moscow.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.23,0:31:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们说他成年的儿子有健康问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They told him his grown son had a health issue
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.35,0:31:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要他立刻回家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}which needed his immediate attention back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.39,0:31:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当这名特工给在苏联的朋友打电话时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When the asset called family friends in the Soviet Union
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.49,0:31:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才确定他儿子生病的事是假的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and established that the story about his son was false,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.38,0:31:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们建议他立即撤离\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we recommended he be exfiltrated immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.69,0:31:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克格勃追他追的很紧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The KGB came after him, hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.57,0:31:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们很幸运\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We got lucky,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.35,0:31:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那名间谍毫发无伤的逃走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and the asset escaped unharmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.84,0:31:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他现在身处美国本土的一间安全屋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's currently in a safe house inside the U.S.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.85,0:31:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但巨锚就没那么幸运了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But GT Weigh, obviously, is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.02,0:31:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是克格勃走了狗屎运\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Either the KGB has gotten extremely lucky of late
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.63,0:31:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就一定是我们有了大麻烦了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}or we have a serious problem on our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.01,0:31:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何  我们遭受了重创\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Whatever it is, we are getting hammered,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.84,0:31:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在苏联布置的情报网络正在遭受破坏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}destroying our eyes and ears inside the Soviet Union.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.72,0:31:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更不用说杀人的那些事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not to mention killing people.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.14,0:31:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事要尽可能先压在局里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This needs to stay in the building as long as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.95,0:31:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总统并不知情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The president doesn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.33,0:31:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媒体当然更不可能知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The press certainly cannot know.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.57,0:31:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须尽快把这事查清\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We need to figure this out fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.17,0:32:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在东苏分部的人马\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your team in S.E. Division
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.41,0:32:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须在我们彻底失去情报来源\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}needs to get their heads back in the game
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.53,0:32:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并输掉这该死的冷战之前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}before we go completely blind
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.82,0:32:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重整旗鼓\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and lose the damn cold war.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.42,0:32:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论什么困难  你都能击败它\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Whatever it is, you will beat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.13,0:32:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我遇到过的最聪明  最坚强\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're the smartest, the toughest,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.83,0:32:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最英勇的女人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The most heroic woman I've ever met.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.98,0:32:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那没问题吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.44,0:32:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的意思是  你真的想要那么坚强\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I mean, do you want a wife who can be that tough,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.76,0:32:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把生活分割出去的妻子吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Who compartmentalizes her life?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.06,0:32:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家庭在一边  工作在另一边\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Family here, work there?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.22,0:32:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且对她最爱的那个人隐瞒很多秘密\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Who keeps secrets from the one person she loves most?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.18,0:32:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们每个人都有秘密  桑迪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We all keep secrets, Sandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.98,0:32:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想象一下如果我们了解凯莉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Imagine how much we'd worry
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.16,0:32:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生活中发生的每一件事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}if we knew every single thing about Kelly's life...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.82,0:32:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道她说的每一句话  该有多担心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...if we knew every word she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.19,0:33:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些时候秘密能让人远离伤害\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sometimes a secret keeps the hurt away.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.95,0:33:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道  我娶你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You know, I married you...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.25,0:33:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为我清楚地知道你要去拯救世界\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}because it was clear to me you were out to save the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.87,0:33:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论付出什么代价  你都会做到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Whatever it took, you would make that happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.58,0:33:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当你真的做到时  我会为你而骄傲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and that I would be proud of you when you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.23,0:33:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个家的每一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Everyone in this family
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.64,0:33:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都知道你为什么要担起这份责任\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}knows why you do what you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.29,0:33:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你自己知道吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But do you know why you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.60,0:33:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你是个勇士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because you are a warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.05,0:33:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保护你的祖国\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Protecting your country.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.87,0:33:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You do it for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.18,0:33:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守护我们的安全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To keep us safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.81,0:33:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回去工作了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have to go back to the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.34,0:33:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不等你睡了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I won't be waiting up.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.08,0:35:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公园里挥手的那个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The man in the park who waved.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.07,0:35:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你整晚都在这里吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You been here all night?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.89,0:35:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是为了警告我们的情报专员离开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He wasn't trying to warn our case officer off the drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.15,0:35:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是要确保情报专员看到他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He was making sure our case officer saw him,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.28,0:35:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意到他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}noticed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.09,0:35:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直没睡过觉  对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You didn't get any sleep, did you?
