Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.25,0:35:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们得到的情报是说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that it got reported back to us
