Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.56,0:35:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样看起来好像他们刚刚知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to make it look like they just figured out
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.05,0:35:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波列修克是个间谍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that Poleshchuk was a spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.84,0:35:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许他们已经怀疑  对他进行了监控\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maybe that they had suspicions, had him under surveillance,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.37,0:35:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他们已经知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but they knew,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.69,0:36:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且已经知道有一阵子了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and they must have known for a while.
