Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.89,0:36:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公园里整个行动只是为了迷惑我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The whole operation in the park is meant to confuse us.
