Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.37,0:36:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们在掩盖更重要的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If they were covering up something more important --
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.86,0:36:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常非常重要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}a lot more important.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.50,0:36:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克格勃在掩盖真正的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}KGB's hiding the true problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.27,0:36:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们能得到局里的情报  亚特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They have an in to the agency, Art.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.74,0:36:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们打入我们内部了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They've cracked us.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.60,0:36:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家  睡个觉  这是命令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Go home, get some sleep. That's an order.
