Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.70,0:37:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大早要不要来一根提提神\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Want to grab an early smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.04,0:37:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我戒了  再不抽了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No. I quit -- for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.47,0:37:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要走了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.58,0:37:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  来半天了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah. Been here a while.
