Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.20,0:37:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.62,0:37:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们会解决的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But we'll get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.21,0:37:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见  里克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}See you, Rick.
