Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.71,0:38:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也喜欢  男孩子们也会喜欢的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Love them. Boys will, too.
