Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.28,0:38:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们有人打入了我们内部\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They got an in to our setup.
